{"tid":1726914,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［超重要］［選舉］ 有父母嘅全部入晒嚟","createTime":"2019-11-16T09:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T14:11:26.000Z","uid":237145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"31052fa59e595ef18d63c73eeece66d78260d8a1","tid":1726914,"uid":237145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:39:22.000Z","msg":"選舉近了<br />\n建制派又會有一班老人院支持者<br />\n平日畀人剝削無視 選舉就帶晒佢地出街飲茶投票<br />\n<br />\n香港人除左要抗衡班假地址太空人外<br />\n老人院有住極大影響力<br />\n<br />\n在此建議<br />\n1.<br />\n選舉日帶返自己屋企人返屋企<br />\n其實都最好陪多啲<br />\n真係子欲養而親不在<br />\n更加唔好令自己父母成為賣港嘅幫兇<br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n如果可以<br />\n帶埋父母老人院嘅單身朋友一齊去飲茶<br />\n單身意思係冇兒冇女冇人理嘅<br />\n<br />\n3.<br />\n父母身份證回收<br />\n如果真係忙到接唔到父母離開老人院<br />\n拎返佢張身份證遲啲先畀返佢啦<br />\n萬一要去醫院 有張副本就搵到紀錄<br />\n唔好畀老院撚呃一定要身份證<br />\n<br />\n暫時剩係諗到呢啲 諗到再加<br />\n<br />\n利申：<br />\n極度建議大家要孝順 唔好重要日子先搵老人家<br />\n你嘅會生有好多野<br />\n但老人家到呢個時候真係得返你地<br />\n想唔想老左啲仔女講住蝗語掉你入老院畀人折磨 之後再見唔到佢哋？<br />\n大家可以行多步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命！<br />\n滅絕掌心雷</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"599bb11350a5aeaf4623b057d6d2a07a0be0722b","tid":1726914,"uid":237145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:02:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"450b0b4172910604495246a40681f11cfd1a7b5c","tid":1726914,"uid":237145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:02:55.000Z","msg":"下星期就選舉<br />\n畀多啲人睇"},{"pid":"ad128cfd7203ce5f897643f536f44be22de40a4a","tid":1726914,"uid":237145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:03:44.000Z","msg":"其實之前出過 <br />\n仲有一個星期再推一下"},{"pid":"d7caa5fe9220edad4ef30b058e633abd8f465987","tid":1726914,"uid":237145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:04:15.000Z","msg":"推 1/10"},{"pid":"9a4797bf73394446d9a82cf06314d96d8baf396a","tid":1726914,"uid":237145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:06:36.000Z","msg":"推 2/10"},{"pid":"3f5774dce80805bd79c445b47954f253fe7ad3d8","tid":1726914,"uid":237145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:06:57.000Z","msg":"推 3/10"},{"pid":"93c6fb60b30988ed17e26cbe037aacdf8a0dd440","tid":1726914,"uid":237145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:07:15.000Z","msg":"推4/10"},{"pid":"d3dcff67650c32511d4f54611dc42ec5b591d047","tid":1726914,"uid":237145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:08:04.000Z","msg":"推5/10"},{"pid":"c2dfec2102721444d76eab74a7c4a0a8ebc5b1a9","tid":1726914,"uid":237145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:10:38.000Z","msg":"推 6/10"},{"pid":"465fa2774d6614ee5ccb822c53f3c53408ec7a15","tid":1726914,"uid":237145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:10:51.000Z","msg":"推 7/10"},{"pid":"a134c2245e8fc762d5bba3598b5466bb029c54c2","tid":1726914,"uid":237145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:11:02.000Z","msg":"推 8/10"},{"pid":"98a837fc94d9bdb1c36113f23809968f262be209","tid":1726914,"uid":237145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:11:14.000Z","msg":"推 9/10"},{"pid":"a8e8add6bfbc6d4322f2c4233e6d456595f45801","tid":1726914,"uid":237145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:11:26.000Z","msg":"推 10/10"}]}